header.gameNote: BASKETBALL HALL OF FAME REVIVAL SERIES

videos.description: Tennessee's Jazmine Massengill snags the ball after a UConn turnover, then lobs to Jordan Horston who lays it in.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Tennessee capitalizes on UConn turnover with Horston layup) 2020/01/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tennessee capitalizes on UConn turnover with Horston layup

videos.description: Tennessee's Rae Burrell fakes the 3-pointer on the perimeter, then drives to the paint and scores plus the foul.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Burrell gets the bucket to drop plus the foul) 2020/01/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Burrell gets the bucket to drop plus the foul

videos.description: Aubrey Griffin leaps and deflects a Tennessee pass, then sprints the length of the court to complete the layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Griffin steals & scores for UConn) 2020/01/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Griffin steals & scores for UConn

videos.description: Aubrey Griffin continues to be a presence for UConn defensively, forcing a turnover which leads to a Christyn Williams layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Griffin forces turnover for UConn, Williams scores) 2020/01/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Griffin forces turnover for UConn, Williams scores

videos.description: Lou Brown dishes a bounce pass between UConn defenders to Rennia Davis, who scores the bucket.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Brown dishes a dime to Davis for Tennessee) 2020/01/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Brown dishes a dime to Davis for Tennessee

videos.description: Crystal Dangerfield scores 14 points and No. 3 UConn uses a dominant third quarter to beat No. 23 Tennessee in their first matchup in 13 years.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCW Highlight (UConn defeats Tennessee in first meeting in 13 years) 2020/1/23 ESHEET SVP SC

videos.headline: UConn defeats Tennessee in first meeting in 13 years
